&lt;p&gt;Vision Warmun 88.0 FM began transmitting on 30 March at 4.30 pm, just pipping Vision Gatton 87.6 FM which started broadcasting at 5 pm.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Welcome to these three new Vision communities! &lt;a href=&quot;http://85.92.78.96/~vision/index.php?option=com_content&amp;amp;view=article&amp;amp;id=7&amp;amp;Itemid=93&quot;&gt;CLICK HERE to see a full list of communities where Vision broadcasts...&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

