&lt;p class=&quot;cmbody&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;The rumours are true! &lt;i&gt;Bob Gass is coming to Australia next month...&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bob's long-awaited return will be in Brisbane on 27 February at Hillsong Church, Rover St, Mt Gravatt (formerly &amp;quot;Garden City Christian Church&amp;quot;). Tickets are available NOW!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;small&gt;NB: tickets are general admission and will be mailed to you.&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This will be a wonderful night to remember! Many Aussies feel as if Bob &amp;amp; his wife Debby are members of their own families. The warmth of their writing in &lt;i&gt;The Word for Today&lt;/i&gt; and Bob's delightful Irish brogue as he reads the daily message on Vision radio are welcomed into hundreds of thousands of homes each day.&lt;/p&gt;

content.fulltext:
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It has been 7 years since his last visit Down Under but Bob's heart for Australia and for God's Word has never flagged. Ian Worby, CEO of UCB, has asked him to bring a special word for our Nation.&lt;/p&gt;
